attributes.title: WILL IT FIT? - Thief Simulator (Pt 2)
attributes.description: Achievement Hunter's most seasoned thieves encounter their biggest challenge. Will it all fit?

attributes.title: PETER PRESSURE - Marvel's Spider-Man: Turf Wars DLC
attributes.description: Achievement Hunter web slings back into Marvel Spider-Man for Hammerhead's new DLC, Turf Wars.

attributes.title: 1-Shot - Resident Evil 2 Demo
attributes.description: Join Michael and Matt as they venture back into the horrifying mansion in Resident Evil 2's "1-Shot Demo".

attributes.title: WE STEAL CHRISTMAS - Thief Simulator (Pt 3) - Let's Watch
attributes.description: The AH thieves are leveling up and taking on bigger jobs. Like safe-cracking, stealing Christmas presents, and doing squats in the yard.

attributes.title: THE MACMILLAN SURREPTITION - Hitman 2: Escalation
attributes.description: The gang do a bit of bush surfing and fish feeding. The also go on to prove that the pen is mightier than the machete.

attributes.title: WE RUINS CHRISTMAS - Thief Simulator (Pt 4)
attributes.description: Everyone's favorite Christmas grinch is back to to steal all the presents from the good little boys and girls in this newest episode of Thief Simulator.

attributes.title: THE DANKEST GAME EVER - Weedcraft Inc.
attributes.description:
Thanks to Devolver Digital for sending us a beta version of Weedcraft Inc. You can add the game to your wishlist here:
https://store.steampowered.com/app/622720/Weedcraft_Inc/

The AH buds take an early look at Weedcraft Inc, a game that (to put it bluntly) is all about growing the Devil's Lettuce. It's dope.

attributes.title: A FROG IN THE POCKET - Hitman 2: Whittleton Creek
attributes.description: The AH crew goes to the suburbs for their next contract. After a warmup of mail theft and rake pranks, they're ready to take out an old man!

attributes.title: WHERE'S THE BABY?! - Pacify
attributes.description: In an effort rid the world of haunting ghost spirits, it's up to our brave AH boys to find lots of wood, a couple of matches, and some bad babies to throw into a furnac-wait, what're they doing?

attributes.title: HACKING AND SMASHING - Thief Simulator (Part 5)
attributes.description:
Achievement Hunter continues their thieving adventures with some more smashing and the newly learned hack skill.

Our other Thief Simulator videos can be found on the Achievement Hunter channel. Watch from the beginning here: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=z0uYB1rwu5g

attributes.title: APOCALYPTIC DEATH FISH - Metro Exodus
attributes.description:
Special thanks to Epic Games for sponsoring this video. You can download Metro Exodus here: https://pixly.go2cloud.org/SH12B

We play Metro Exodus and experiences what it's like when your common animal gets radiated in a post-apocalyptic world. Spoiler alert: large fish

attributes.title: PETTY THEFT AUTO - Thief Simulator (Part 6)
attributes.description: We're back in Thief Simulator, where we're making robbing houses look like child's play. It's time to steal some cars (or at the very least, parts of cars)!

attributes.title: GREAT DOUBLE BUST HEIST - Thief Simulator (Part 7)
attributes.description: We've stolen plenty in Thief Simulator, but this week's goal is super busty. Ryan gets a handful of bust, then attempts to fit two busts in his trunk. Delicately.

attributes.title: WE GOT A NEW VAN! - Thief Simulator (Part 8)
attributes.description: We're "riskin' the biscuits" in this episode of Thief Simulator. Ryan has a new van and lots of  trunk space! He's itchin' to throw a bunch of antiques and TVs into it. Could this be Ryan's most successful thieving ever?

attributes.title: Thief Simulator Uncut (Parts 9-13)
attributes.description: Enjoy parts 9 through 13 of Thief Simulator in their entirety! We go for the mustang, the busts, and find a little bit of ourselves along the way.

attributes.title: Thief Simulator Parts 14 - 17 (Gameplay)
attributes.description: Parts 14 through 17 of Thief Simulator are here! Let's steal busts, grab some art, and see what else Vinny has in store for us!

attributes.title: Hobo: Tough Life Parts 1 - 2 (Gameplay)
attributes.description: Parts 1 and 2 of Hobo: Tough Life is here! Watch AH scavenge some junk, find some more junk, and sell some other junk!

attributes.title: HOW TO CONQUER CHINA - Total War: Three Kingdoms
attributes.description:
Thanks to Total War and Creative Assembly for sponsoring this video! You can check out the game at http://bit.ly/TotalWarAH.
In this Total War: Three Kingdoms gameplay, AH leads Cao Cao to gather his units and do battle across ancient China.

attributes.title: The Long Dark Parts 1 - 4 (Gameplay)
attributes.description: Parts 1 through 4 of The Long Dark have arrived! After a devastating plane crash, AH hangs out in a cave, try to woo an old blind lady, and crack open a bank vault!

attributes.title: The Long Dark Parts 5 - 8 (Gameplay)
attributes.description: Parts 5 through 8 of The Long Dark have arrived! This time our pants freeze, but our spirit burns hotter than ever!

attributes.title: Layers of Fear 2 Parts 1-4 (Gameplay)
attributes.description: The Boo Crew assembles to play Layers of Fear 2. In these first four parts, we play through all of Act 1: The Unmooring.

attributes.title: THE VANISHING TV - Thief Simulator (New Game Plus)
attributes.description: Get 15% off your first pair at http://meundies.com/ahlivestream. In this Thief Sim gameplay, we dive into New Game Plus! Can we rob enough to get us that illusive cloaking device?

attributes.title: Layers of Fear 2 Parts 5-8 (Gameplay)
attributes.description: The Boo Crew is back with more Layers of Fear 2! In these next four parts we get through Act 2: The Hunt.

attributes.title: Layers of Fear 2 Act 3 (Gameplay)
attributes.description: In this Layers of Fear 2 gameplay, we finish Act 3: Bloody Roots!

attributes.title: LOOK AT MY BABY LEGS - Trover Saves the Universe
attributes.description: We're collecting all power babies in this Trover Saves the Universe Gameplay.

attributes.title: A FISTFUL OF OINKS - Don't Starve: Hamlet
attributes.description:
Thanks to Klei for sponsoring this video.
Find out more about Don't Starve and Klei's additional games here: http://bit.ly/DontStarveHamlet_LetsPlay

We're playing the new Don't Starve: Hamlet DLC where we discover a lost town of aristocratic Pigmen. What could go wrong?

attributes.title: The Clown Heist - Hitman 2: The Bank
attributes.description: It's Hitman 2 gameplay in The Bank! Get the clown suit! It's time to steal.

attributes.title: Space Janitors - Void Bastards
attributes.description: In Void Bastards we play as space criminals fighting ghost children, robot cats, and space janitors.

attributes.title: Detective Sad Eyes - The Sinking City
attributes.description: We're sinking our feet into The Sinking City. What Cthulhu monsters await Detective Sad Eyes in this gameplay?

attributes.title: Thief Simulator Parts 18 - 20 (Gameplay)
attributes.description: Parts 18 through 20 of Thief Simulator are here! It's DLC time and, more importantly, it's payback time. Vinny, we're coming for you.

attributes.title: Thief Simulator Parts 21 - 22 (Gameplay)
attributes.description: Parts 21 and 22 of Thief Simulator are here! It's time to continue the DLC by learning some new, explosive skills. Vinny, we're coming for you!

attributes.title: Slow-Mo Banana Trick Shot! - My Friend Pedro
attributes.description: We're getting all the trick shot style points in this My Friend Pedro gameplay!

attributes.title: Hoverboard Drone Strike - Just Cause 4: Danger Rising
attributes.description: We take an early look at new DLC in Just Cause 4!

attributes.title: 5 Characters, 5 Players - Man of Medan: Prologue & Act 1
attributes.description:
In this gameplay, we play the prologue and Act 1 of Man of Medan.

It's time for spooky gameplay in the new horror game, Man of Medan, made by the creators of Until Dawn. With five players each taking control of the game's five protagonists, we're hoping to avoid all the deaths we can.

attributes.title: Courting KFC's Colonel - I Love You, Colonel Sanders!
attributes.description:
Thanks to KFC for sponsoring this video. You can pick up your copy of I Love You Colonel Sanders! A Finger Lickin’ Good Dating Simulator here: https://bit.ly/2kBX3dl 

Michael, Fiona, and Lindsay eat fried chicken with Mac and Cheese and play I Love You Colonel Sanders! A Finger Lickin’ Good Dating Simulator.

attributes.title: A Boarding Party - Man of Medan: Act 2, Part 1
attributes.description:
In this gameplay, we play the first half of Act 2 of Man of Medan.

The spooky gameplay continues in the horror game, Man of Medan. So far all five characters are alive. Here's to hoping we can avoid more deaths as we begin Act 2.

attributes.title: Avoiding a Premonition - Man of Medan: Act 2, Part 2
attributes.description:
In this gameplay, we finish Act 2 of Man of Medan.

The spooky gameplay continues in the horror game, Man of Medan. So far all five characters are alive. Here's to hoping we can avoid more deaths as we finish Act 2

attributes.title: Worst Vacation Ever - Hitman 2: The Last Resort
attributes.description: We're back with Hitman 2! In this new DLC, we take a trip to Haven Island.

attributes.title: Slugging Our Way to Victory - Hitman 2: Escalation
attributes.description: We pacify everyone with a bat in this a spooky Hitman 2: Escalation gameplay.

attributes.title: The Worst Explosives Team Ever - Hitman 2: Escalation
attributes.description: The crew is putting the pain in propane in this Hitman 2 escalation gameplay.

attributes.title: We Train the Next CHAMPION! - Pokémon Sword & Shield
attributes.description: We pick our starter Pokémon! It's time for some Pokémon Sword gameplay!
